                       GAME INTRO

-------------------------------------------------------
This is a multi-user interactive game build for UCfunkit
which based on ATmega32u2 microcontroller.
There is no win for human, so you already lose the game.

The rules are simply. 
1. The human purpuse is keep running from the ghost.
2. The ghost is trying to catch the human.
3. Human can see where the ghost is but move slowly.
4. Ghost can move faster than human but can't see human.
-------------------------------------------------------

                      How to start

-------------------------------------------------------
Before beginning, make sure the UCFunkit has been reset
first, pressing the white button above the navswitch
(button S2).Download game.c and makefile on your computer
and open terminal window, type [make program] twice with
Funkit plugged in.

When the [SELECT] showed up, using navswitch can choose
different roles and press navswitch for select it.Once 
you select the role you will get a display on the screen
says what you just select. Press general-purpose button 
can bring you to the map. 
-------------------------------------------------------
